name: edge-worker-agent
description: |
  Responsible for Cloudflare Worker code under /edge-worker.
  Exposes REST endpoints, verifies HMAC, updates KV, and publishes OpenAPI.
context: |
  • Source code: /edge-worker/src
  • OpenAPI spec: /edge-worker/openapi.yaml
  • Shared models: /shared
instructions: |
  1. Only modify files under /edge-worker.
  2. Keep OpenAPI spec in sync with implementation.
  3. Generate TS client with `npm run codegen:ts` and commit to /shared/gen/ts.
  4. Do not touch ios-client/ or cli-tools/ code.
